ComicInfo.Summary:
Gammazons from Galaxy G!: FemForce invades the Gammazons' ship, freeing their captive members and ending the Gammazon threat. Later, Nightveil asks the team how they plan to explain the existence of Garganta to General Gordon, who ordered the team to destroy her.
Horror House: Arriving for her real estate appointment with Miss Martin, the realtor, Katie is unaware that a deadly trap has been laid for her.
Luger Laughs Last!: Jennifer Burke, the new Ms. Victory, and Colt separately search for Burke's mother, Joan Wayne, the previous Miss Victory who is now Femforce renegade Rad. Successfully concocting a new youth restorative, V-50, for her unknown benefactor, Joan is shocked when her old WWII nemesis, Lady Luger, uses it to become young again and begin her long-time plan of revenge against her.
